---
title: Powerfull website you should know
description: Discover a curated list of powerful websites you should know about. Stay updated with the best tools, resources, and services on the internet to enhance your productivity, knowledge, and entertainment.
image: https://powerfull-website-you-should-know.netlify.app/assets/images/meta-image.jpg
layout: "base.njk"
---

<section class="mt-10 mb-4">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="heroBanner">
      <div
        class="heroBanner_image d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="heroBanner_text">
          <h1>Discover the Web's Best Kept Secrets</h1>
          <p>
            Unlock a curated list of powerful websites that will transform your
            online experience. From productivity tools to hidden gems, explore
            the must-know resources of the internet.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="heroBanner_overlay"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="mt-12 mb-4 tools">
  <div class="container">
    <h4 class="text-center fw-bold mb-6">Featured Tools</h4>
    <div class="tools-container">
      
      {% for post in collections.post %}
      <div class="card border-0 rounded-0 h-100">
        <div class="card-header border-0" style="background-color: {{ post.data.backgroundColor }}">
          <img
            src="{{ post.data.image }}"
            alt="{{ post.data.imageAlt }}"
            class="img-fluid card-header_image" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h6 class="card-title">{{ post.data.name }}</h6>
          <p class="card-text">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer border-0 bg-light">
          <a href="{{ post.data.link }}" class="card-link" target="_blank">
            Visit <i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
